/*
-Install the Costura.Fody NuGet package and update the Fody NuGet package:
  PM> Install-Package Fody
  PM> Install-Package Costura.Fody

-check it has been added to your project.

-create new file in root of your project with name "FodyWeavers.xml" and copy following 4 lones to it:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Weavers xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="FodyWeavers.xsd">
  <Costura />
</Weavers>

-rebuild

-if error in: None Update
  change it to: None Include


*/

